<bibRefCitation author="Rousse P. &amp; Villemant C. &amp; Seyrig A." box="[607,825,368,394]" pageId="103" pageNumber="104" pagination="1 - 38" refId="ref43162" refString="Rousse P., Villemant C. &amp; Seyrig A. 2013. Ichneumonid wasps from Madagascar. VI. The genus Pristomerus (Hymenoptera: Ichneumonidae: Cremastinae). European Journal of Taxonomy 49: 1 - 38. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.5852 / ejt. 2013.49" type="journal article" year="2013">
